description:
Glizzy Royale is an ambitious and groundbreaking Solana gaming project with one major goal in mind: to make blockchain gaming fun. Our game is a third-person shooter that will be releasing a Battle Royale in the near future. In the meantime, we have already released a 1v1 arena mode which can be downloaded below. Our roadmap contains our build plan at a high level. Our genesis NFT collection will contain 4000 unique Glizzies which have been genetically modified to become super soldiers. The holders of this genesis collection will have the opportunity to earn our native utility token, $GLIZZY, through staking. 

 We believe that achieving our goal (of making a fun blockchain game) involves four core tenets: an engaging and smooth game, incredible art, a large network of users, and a robust token economy.
name: Glizzy Royale
